inoma, as well as a marker for intratubular germ cell neoplasia.9</div>          </td>        </tr>      </table>    </div>    <div class="antibody-link-button">      <a href="https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/127/p53_DO7" target="_blank" title="View Cell Marque Product Page">        <img src="#WORKSPACE_FILES#assets/images/Scientific/suppliers/Cell_Marque/cell_marque-logo.png" alt="View Product" class="product-link-image">      </a>    </div>  </div></div>','p53 antibody labels poorly differentiated colon adenocarcinoma in a nuclear pattern.','https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/127/p53_DO7','#','https://www.cellmarque.com/cmsial-images/TH_453M-9-ihc-01.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,to_date('24-APR-26','DD-MON-RR'),null,'_cm-127-p53-do7-81162EE8',null,null,null,null,'Cell Marque','DIS-0001','PRG-0001','PTY-0003',null,null,'Syntec Scientific','CM/127/p53_DO7');
