diagnosis of primary and metastatic tumors.1-4 Note:This product is in obsolescence.Uroplakin III (AU-1)is available as an alternative.</div>          </td>        </tr>      </table>    </div>    <div class="antibody-link-button">      <a href="https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/2097/Uroplakin-III_SP73" target="_blank" title="View Cell Marque Product Page">        <img src="#WORKSPACE_FILES#assets/images/Scientific/suppliers/Cell_Marque/cell_marque-logo.png" alt="View Product" class="product-link-image">      </a>    </div>  </div></div>','Uroplakin III antibody labels the superficial layer of cells in transitional cell carcinoma of the bladder.','https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/2097/Uroplakin-III_SP73','#','https://www.cellmarque.com/cmsial-images/TH_345R-1-ihc-01.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,to_date('24-APR-26','DD-MON-RR'),null,'_cm-2097-uroplakin-iii-sp73-219AD634',null,null,null,null,'Cell Marque','DIS-0001','PRG-0001','PTY-0003',null,null,'Syntec Scientific','CM/2097/Uroplakin-III_SP73');
