roduct Page">        <img src="#WORKSPACE_FILES#assets/images/Scientific/suppliers/Cell_Marque/cell_marque-logo.png" alt="View Product" class="product-link-image">      </a>    </div>  </div></div>','Acute myeloid leukemia cells are stained with CD16 antibody in a strong cytoplasmic pattern.','https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/2155/CD16_SP175','#','https://www.cellmarque.com/cmsial-images/TH_116R-1-ihc-01.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,to_date('24-APR-26','DD-MON-RR'),null,'_cm-2155-cd16-sp175-D72B73D4',null,null,null,null,'Cell Marque','DIS-0001','PRG-0001','PTY-0003',null,null,'Syntec Scientific','CM/2155/CD16_SP175');
