nonvascular tumors (excluding hematopoietic neoplasms) has not been observed. Note:This product is in obsolescence.CD31 (JC70)is available as an alternative.</div>          </td>        </tr>      </table>    </div>    <div class="antibody-link-button">      <a href="https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/3151/CD31_EP78" target="_blank" title="View Cell Marque Product Page">        <img src="#WORKSPACE_FILES#assets/images/Scientific/suppliers/Cell_Marque/cell_marque-logo.png" alt="View Product" class="product-link-image">      </a>    </div>  </div></div>','CD31 (EP78) on hemangioendothelioma.','https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/3151/CD31_EP78','#','https://www.cellmarque.com/cmsial-images/TH_131R-2-ihc-01.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,to_date('24-APR-26','DD-MON-RR'),null,'_cm-3151-cd31-ep78-8B287696',null,null,null,null,'Cell Marque','DIS-0001','PRG-0001','PTY-0003',null,null,'Syntec Scientific','CM/3151/CD31_EP78');
