an survive in harsh environments such as the digestive and respiratory tracts, to provide protection against microbes that multiply in body secretions. It is useful when identifying multiple myeloma and plasmacytomas.1-3</div>          </td>        </tr>      </table>    </div>    <div class="antibody-link-button">      <a href="https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/3154/IgA_EP170" target="_blank" title="View Cell Marque Product Page">        <img src="#WORKSPACE_FILES#assets/images/Scientific/suppliers/Cell_Marque/cell_marque-logo.png" alt="View Product" class="product-link-image">      </a>    </div>  </div></div>','IgA (EP170) on tonsil.','https://www.cellmarque.com/antibodies/CM/3154/IgA_EP170','#','https://www.cellmarque.com/cmsial-images/TH_267R-1-ihc-01.jpg',null,null,null,null,null,null,to_date('24-APR-26','DD-MON-RR'),null,'_cm-3154-iga-ep170-DD9E919C',null,null,null,null,'Cell Marque','DIS-0001','PRG-0001','PTY-0003',null,null,'Syntec Scientific','CM/3154/IgA_EP170');
